{
  "stem": "16106.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "But I had my book.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I had-- there somehow, I got my books, by Stefan Zweig.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And I read that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Yeah, life in the concentration camp was very interesting once you got used to the tempo and the rhythm of things, what you should do, what you cannot do, what is good for you, and what-- you learn that very fast.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "For example, when you were on appell or selections--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Early in the morning, we had to get out fast, fast from the things and, and line up and were counted by an SS person and by Gerda.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you, you better stand next to a good-looking person, not to a Muselmann.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know the expression Muselmann?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You had better not stand next to a Muselmann.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because what can happen, the Muselmann is taken, and you get-- you get with him, go with him somehow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Get next to a good-looking person, next to a young person, next to a strong person.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And be on your own.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If you are loyal, you have less chances.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I learned that very fast.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then we were assigned jobs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I worked on the [GERMAN], on the [GERMAN], on the airport.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were building something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, we were took the lorry going, took it back, whatever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And, and I don't know what we did, highways.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And Feldinger was our, our-- Feldinger, that German guy was the one who was responsible for us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He had a little hut.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There he sat.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there, a, a, a girl made for him cup of coffee.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "To work with that, in that part, was a very good thing, didn't have to be outside.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I-- we went every morning out there and sang, going there and coming home, and sang.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All sorts of things.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
